.TH "sata_pmp_set_lpm" 9 "sata_pmp_set_lpm" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
sata_pmp_set_lpm \- configure LPM for a PMP link
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" sata_pmp_set_lpm
.BI "(struct ata_link *link "  ","
.BI "enum ata_lpm_policy policy "  ","
.BI "unsigned hints "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "link" 12
PMP link to configure LPM for
.IP "policy" 12
target LPM policy
.IP "hints" 12
LPM hints

Configure LPM for \fIlink\fP.  This function will contain any PMP
specific workarounds if necessary.

LOCKING:
EH context.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, -errno on failure.
